{"tid":1973750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急幫推]香港口罩大踢爆！幕後居心叵測？","createTime":"2020-04-15T11:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T11:39:08.000Z","uid":306111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5eb1d4e13de133b75c9243adc5dbd406561f293","tid":1973750,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:17:08.000Z","msg":"－《序》<br />\n話說，大約三個星期前，我老母同班師奶朋友放工行街，見到有個街站叫人填張form就可以領取消毒噴霧一支同埋預留所謂香港製造嘅口罩。<br />\n老母返到屋企梗係同我開心share呢件事，跟住就比我發現奇怪嘅地方......<br />\n<br />\n－《懷疑》<br />\n首先，搞街站個團體叫做「深水埗營地」。深水埗都有營地？你無聽錯，佢哋就係叫「深水埗營地」（網址：<a href=\"https://sspcamp.hk/tc/About_index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsspcamp.hk%2Ftc%2FAbout_index.php&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQJ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=721a9b53\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspcamp.hk/tc/About_index.php</a> ）。呢個組織真係聞所未聞，網絡上資料極少，突然話有<strong>香港口罩</strong>賣(180/盒)，令我起咗疑心。接著落嚟嘅呢件事令我ip都唔使check就知佢哋嘅目的。<br />\n<br />\n－《洩露》<br />\n我將我嘅猜疑同老母講，並且問佢填form有無比咩個人資料佢。老母話：「下！唔撚係呃錢掛，我比咗名、地址、身份證頭幾隻字、電話...<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呀！仲有！佢問我係咪選民</span></strong></span>。」喺嗰一刻我已經肯定呢個組織唔簡單。<br />\n<br />\n－《初探》<br />\n喺某日，<strong>香港製造嘅口罩</strong>終於有貨！（呢隻<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">口罩名叫「M plus」</span></span></strong>相信市面已經有炒家。）老母叫我拿拿林去拎。佢哋報俾我哋嘅地址係「華富商業大廈1601室」。上到去發現根本唔係「深水埗營地」，而係一間叫「Green hill」嘅公司。交收過程都叫順利，公司內籠擺咗勁多紙皮箱，可能都係呢隻口罩。之後我就急急腳走人，決定返屋企慢慢研究。<br />\n<br />\n－《揭發》<br />\n原來！「華富商業大廈1601室」同時share緊幾間公司/機構名（包括：深水埗營地、Green hill、M plus口罩製造公司、<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共和國之旅青年築夢基金</span></span></strong>) 。啊哈，事情發展嚟到呢度，相信大家都知咩事。<br />\n<br />\n總結：懷疑「深水埗營地」利用街坊貪小便宜心態，出售自稱香港製造口罩，套取個人資料作唔知咩嘅用途（唔猜測啦）。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好貪心，注意呢幾個月有無人搵你套取個人資料呀！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\nbtw老母最後話「嚇死，好彩唔係呃錢，唔緊要啦係紅底就，我恨不得捐俾佢添啦！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我微微一笑，心卻是那麼痛。<br />\n－《完》<br />\n謝謝大家。"},{"pid":"d2c89e3fde5dfe390044ebaaf2730597acef10fc","tid":1973750,"uid":303468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8537ccce4fa31252754b8de8c2f7f43912b880","tid":1973750,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:21:03.000Z","msg":"口罩圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zfP8gu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zfP8gu.jpg&h=9e4604e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVA4W9R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVA4W9R.jpg&h=f4c19170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gg1S526.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgg1S526.jpg&h=6c4177ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bbba8eb910c8bbab421ceb750e64a07e9aa9bc1","tid":1973750,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"未聽過呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f9f2b7f407ac98c4668da4978624b84bac4f5e","tid":1973750,"uid":306111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bbba8eb910c8bbab421ceb750e64a07e9aa9bc1","tid":1973750,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"未聽過呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T11:39:08.000Z","msg":"唔知點解好少資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}